    {
        "content": "<p>Yup, that's by design. Otherwise you take on yourself the burden of writing a tactic that can decide <code>a^3 + b^3 = c^3</code>. And such problems are pretty hard.</p>",
        "id": 480586256,
        "sender_full_name": "Johan Commelin",
        "timestamp": 1730788505
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>In this case, replacing the <code>rw</code> line with <code>ring_nf at *</code> works. Or you can have <code>have := mul_comm b c</code> to give omega an additional fact.</p>",
